JUDY WOODRUFF: Authorities in
Saint Louis County, Missouri,
imposed a new state of emergency

16:24.817 --> 16:30.089
today after police critically
wounded an 18-year-old black man
overnight.

16:30.089 --> 16:34.961
It happened at the end of
protests in the town of Ferguson
marking the death of Michael

16:34.961 --> 16:41.133
Brown one year ago. Police said
a late-night demonstration got
rowdy, and Tyrone Harris

16:41.133 --> 16:44.770
Jr. and others opened fire on
them. They said officers shot
back, wounding Harris.

